#

Pan-Seared Duck Breast with Cherry Reduction and Roasted Brussels Sprouts

$30
600 kcal
Difficulty: 75%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-free

Tags:

gourmetmain coursedinner

Description

A gourmet dish featuring succulent duck breast with a rich cherry sauce, complemented by crispy roasted Brussels sprouts.

Ingredients

  • Duck breast: 2 pieces
  • Cherries: 1 cup
  • Red wine: 1/2 cup
  • Chicken stock: 1/4 cup
  • Shallots: 2, finely chopped
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Brussels sprouts: 1 lb
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Thyme: 1 teaspoon, fresh
  • Sugar: 1 tablespoon
